# Product API Tests
# Use the environment selector in the HTTP Client to switch between environments

### Get all products
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Get product by ID (replace 1 with the actual ID)
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

### Get product by ID (non-existent ID to test error handling)
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/products/999
Accept: application/json
